BUSINESS RULE SPECIFICATIONS

RULE INFORMATION

Statement:  Two classes cannot take place In the same room during the same time slot.

Constraint: The Time_block For 2 different classes can only be the same If the classes have different locations.

Type:     Database Oriented:     [X] 
          Application Oriented   _ 

Category: Field Specific:        _ 
          Relationship Specific: [X]

Test On:  Insert:                [X] 
          Delete:                _ 
          Update:                [X]


STRUCTURES AFFECTED

Field Names: location, Meeting_times

Table Names: Class, Locations


FIELD ELEMENTS AFFECTED

Physical Elements: Data Type:           _ 
                   Length:              _ 
                   Character Support:   _ 

Logical Elements:  Key Type:            _ 
                   Key Structure:       _ 
                   Uniqueness:          [X] 
                   Null Support:        _ 
                   Values Entered By:   _ 
                   Range of Values:     [X] 
                   Edit Rule:           [X] 


RELATIONSHIP CHARACTERISTICS AFFECTED

    Deletion rule:              [X]
    Type of participation:      _
    Degree of participation:    _

    
ACTION TAKEN

When classes are created the system assures that there are no conflicts in settingf among classes by not allowing 2 different classes for the same time and the same location.


